OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fand outbreaks of rain over Shetland
OL,7,Fthrough the evening but mainly dry
OL,8,Fover Orkney. Further rain will then
OL,9,Fspread north across all parts
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FOvernight rain clearing away
OL,13,Fin the morning with some haar at first
OL,14,Facross Shetland. Then mainly dry with
OL,15,Fsome hazy sunshine and just the odd
OL,16,Fshower possible. A bit warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
